# Weather App

Simple web application to display current weather data.

## Overview

This project is a small web application that fetches and displays weather information for a given location.
It was developed as part of my practice in web development.

## Technologies

* JavaScript
* HTML
* CSS

## Features

* Search for weather by location
* Display of temperature and weather conditions
* Simple and responsive user interface

## Purpose

The goal of this project was to improve my understanding of working with APIs and building interactive web applications.
